If someone's looking to get into the series I might not pick this one to use as their first as it's a bit complex compared to the others. It's so satisfying seeing the drinks mix together as you layer the ingredients, and playing for too long makes me want a coffee. I'm also enjoying the ingredients for this game, they're very unique without ever feeling ridiculous, and I'm always excited to see what I'll unlock next.
